title: I AM NOT WHERE I WANT TO BE, BUT I'LL GET THERE
itunes:title: I AM NOT WHERE I WANT TO BE, BUT I'LL GET THERE
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
I'm not where I want to be, but I'll get there. You may not be where YOU want to be, but look how FAR you have come. Whatever you are working towards, I promise you, if you KEEP PUSHING, you are going to get it. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever featuring Coach Pain. Produced and edited by Motiversity.
